{"tid":1922293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［重開］信報認證：駱惠寧最大挑戰係9月立會，佢非常關心","createTime":"2020-03-12T13:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T00:52:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2b075e2ce421a9bcdfd43754eaf137a398b23a","tid":1922293,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:03:15.000Z","msg":"中聯辦主任駱惠寧走馬上任後最大挑戰，莫過於今年9月立法會選舉，能否協調各方助建制派力挽狂瀾，阻止民主派搶佔議會過半席位，成為大眾焦點。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，駱主任對選舉一事非常關心，惟未有太多干預部署，仍交由中聯辦副主任何靖操盤。「西環」為求交出漂亮成績表，當然希望在不同界別爭取最多議席，但有建制政黨憂慮，中聯辦若在地區直選布陣過於進取，該陣營隨時人仰馬翻⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2393461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2393461&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=a583a5e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2393461</a><br />\n<br />\n後面講原因：如果佢大幅改變<br />\n衰咗要孭鑊<br />\n所以傾向唔大改唔上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個仲話唔重要唔好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c74e241a30be04534f5050f6e27b5b962e662a","tid":1922293,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"我想睇佢仆街<br />\n所以記得投票"},{"pid":"95e75da87fb46ccb65bb0e900103cf02a636de39","tid":1922293,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:55:07.000Z","msg":"我比較關心佢幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03260e674783bebb2f39ff1dcbf2094326893c5d","tid":1922293,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gi